/*
 *   - x axis is always time.
 *   - data is given as [{time: TIMESTAMP, value: VALUE, label: LABEL}]
 *   - TIMESTAMP is in UNIX_MS
 *   - @TODO:
          • multiple lines as [[{time: TIMESTAMP, value: VALUE}, ...], [{time: TIMESTAMP, value: VALUE}, ...] ...])
 *
 *
